{"tid":1469842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地而家既敵人，70年前將國民黨打到無左大半江山，靠既就係滲透同分化","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T05:46:44.000Z","uid":196536,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b6486baf9257b732a00ea3b6a7a4d58c50bcac8b","tid":1469842,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"實在無需要捉鬼。<br />\n敵人就係想我地陷入捉鬼既泥沼入面，忙於內鬥猜疑而不做正事。<br />\n佢地最厲害就係玩陰招，等我地疑神疑鬼。<br />\n國民黨輸左，香港人會輸嗎？我唔知。<br />\n但我地有前車之鑑。<br />\n緊記be water之初心，和勇相濟之初心，不割。<br />\n出黎抗爭，錢可以唔帶，腦一定要帶！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要有獨立思考能力，不可以人云亦云。<br />\n緊記幾個大原則：<br />\n唔打記者 唔打急救 唔衝禁區<br />\n唔打遊客<br />\n唔態度惡劣<br />\n有違以上都唔係同路人，防範即可</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，保持正能量，毋忘初衷！</span>"},{"pid":"9018df1f56315b81ccad05d18235535cdb21e609","tid":1469842,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:24.000Z","msg":"入黎負皮啦一毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1d96407f59974b9ea844f06f2dd7301022d28e","tid":1469842,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>一直都叫人唔好睇小CCP<br />\n<br />\n謝謝 你個標題好警世！<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加推<br />\n唔該黎個萬人接機<br />\n<br />\n小妹誠邀大家今晚來接我機！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469801</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba99094d31bbfe7cf944e7c5914b122a9a9f79f6","tid":1469842,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e2e0e7635e315e6fb311d1bad7e2bcbc04d2036c","tid":1469842,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baf70360b4c141dd8b56293d48d0b41b571ab653","tid":1469842,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:32:45.000Z","msg":"推👍🏽"},{"pid":"e6ca071ec3ad79615b4d1c5529